{"tid":401144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"落台啦沈祖堯屌你老母","createTime":"2017-09-15T11:24:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T17:02:35.000Z","uid":33307,"like":5,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d49a94d91b94387798b73539506e47943e026bc8","tid":401144,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T11:24:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中大等多間大學校園和民主牆，近期先後出現港獨宣傳品。中大校長沈祖堯主動絡傳媒今日下午開記者會，表示香港是中國不可分割的一部分，要求學生會盡快移除所有港獨宣傳品，否則校方會移除有關物品。他又代表中大，向所有被校內民主牆上言論被冒犯的人致歉。"},{"pid":"5e09d909f692a7bb2da8c3697f0e7d386adee65c","tid":401144,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T12:22:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da545e7a4b9fcfad7ea326118c97910fd47ca396","tid":401144,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T12:38:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f20a76859ff065eb25464286b31bc7da690fba13","tid":401144,"uid":126510,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T17:01:47.000Z","msg":"呢条友同雲膠一樣<br />\n凈係識講D好聽既野搏下民望<br />\n但行政上實際根本做唔到野<br />\n中大個排名係咁跌<br />\n又開深圳分校稀釋學位<br />\nON99"},{"pid":"7134e21899c323bd61962e0cc6af4186c5d85620","tid":401144,"uid":126510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T17:02:35.000Z","msg":"呢条友同雲膠一樣<br />\n凈係識講D好聽既野搏下民望<br />\n但行政上實際根本做唔到野<br />\n中大個排名係咁跌<br />\n又開深圳分校稀釋學位<br />\nON99"}]}